                "invention-title": [
                    "Air tightness detection system for hydrogen energy pipeline production",
                    "一种氢能管道生产用气密性检测系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an air tightness detection system for hydrogen energy pipeline production, which comprises a feeding mechanism and a detection mechanism, and is characterized in that the feeding mechanism comprises a supporting seat, the top end of the supporting seat is rotatably provided with a first rotating shaft through a first support, the first rotating shaft is fixedly provided with a feeding turntable, and the feeding turntable is provided with a plurality of pipeline clamping mechanisms; the detection mechanism comprises a detection plug. According to the invention, the feeding turntable rotates to convey each pipeline to the position of the detection plug in sequence, the first cylinder drives the detection plug to be inserted into the to-be-detected pipeline, the detection plug and the feeding turntable are both provided with airtight rubber pads, two ends of the pipeline are blocked through extrusion, and high-pressure gas is injected into the pipeline. The pressure change is detected through the pressure sensor, if the pressure does not drop quickly, the air tightness of the pipeline is qualified, the purpose of quick feeding is achieved through the feeding turntable, and the detection efficiency is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氢能管道生产用气密性检测系统，包括送料机构和检测机构，所述送料机构包括支撑座，支撑座的顶端通过第一支架转动安装有第一转轴，第一转轴上固定有送料转盘，送料转盘上安装有多个管道夹持机构，检测机构包括检测插头。本发明通过送料转盘转动，来依次的将各个管道运送至检测插头位置，通过第一气缸带动检测插头插入到待检测的管道内，检测插头上已经送料转盘上均设有气密胶垫，通过挤压将管道的两端堵住，并朝向管道内部冲入高压气体，并保持密封，通过压力传感器检测压强变化，若压力不会迅速的下降，则表示管道气密性合格，通过送料转盘达到快速送料的目的，提高检测效率。"
                }
            ]
